{"tid":1843043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護人員其實唔需要罷工，只要聲明只會優先服務香港人（內有原因）！","createTime":"2020-01-26T04:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T05:10:49.000Z","uid":118346,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"870152737c94349569d79acfabdf970b6f46ade7","tid":1843043,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"罷工：會俾政府和左膠批評為私利<br />\n優先服務香港人：外國來的遊客（不理是中國還是其他，記住呢個係重點，唔好俾人有籍口批評），全部分流到隔離區4,5個鐘先醫，優先服務香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f739c135140c19cea93a0e52517522d69d6b5c29","tid":1843043,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:45:54.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"6e86bb83a38636ce52ebc7854cbd1aaca482a0e0","tid":1843043,"uid":118346,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"按章工作<br />\n<br />\n上司叫自己要照顧個兩條友呢，哦完佢就繼續跟工作守則，優先服務香港人而香港醫療系統爆棚，淨係服務香港人都唔會夠時間了，所以就係永遠都係服務香港人。服務完香港人，先會有空檔服務個兩條大陸友。<br />\n<br />\n服務香港人呢，係永遠服務唔會有完結一日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f38bdb37af0f4bbcd3ce53401f58609f78d17e","tid":1843043,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2192e1e86def127a655657b3f9ccf1b99c8ffc29","tid":1843043,"uid":261756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08379be05977c3d222d69ac2a91f10ca3b205a9a","tid":1843043,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8580a9c2d8a990cb10f804c5906155141f6d9e7","tid":1843043,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17ed1bc51195ebd92ef447dfab461f0f9c99563","tid":1843043,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8095f63c19a4838963b0aa4ad7e231bd1c463def","tid":1843043,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"剩係唔理中國<br />\n外國理 吹啊"},{"pid":"0d50c4ece555d05082dec67c008ead236b082476","tid":1843043,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"全部分流到隔離區4,5<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日</span></span>先醫"},{"pid":"c9271cddf05b9c5b18e949758ef1e563f2883778","tid":1843043,"uid":272603,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"有條友係你隔離叫救命<br />\n你忍唔忍到唔救佢<br />\n你真係當醫護無良心 小悅悅大陸人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷工 D人就自然唔去醫院<br />\n非緊急服務就停曬佢啦"},{"pid":"1db97015b6fd7d4a7c8eabbae2a121a0cd46ef02","tid":1843043,"uid":200019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷工係用醫療系統停罷嚟威脅政府封關<br />\n你醫療系統唔完全停頓，勉強運作，到時政府直係理撚得你<br />\n<br />\n預防勝於治療，冠狀病毒無藥醫，永遠都係防止擴散&gt;醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n如果我中招，醫護為咗拯救更多香港人，罷工而放棄我呢個已受感染嘅病患，我死都唔割罷工。"},{"pid":"56aed62f2fef3c3d5630b4e16512a7dbd90c006f","tid":1843043,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9271cddf05b9c5b18e949758ef1e563f2883778","tid":1843043,"uid":272603,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"有條友係你隔離叫救命<br />\n你忍唔忍到唔救佢<br />\n你真係當醫護無良心 小悅悅大陸人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷工 D人就自然唔去醫院<br />\n非緊急服務就停曬佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01